comments.body:
@carljmosca, this is a really terrific addition for Podman.  I know I left a number of comments, but most were at the nit level.  The overall content is exceptional.

Two things to watch for in case I missed them.  It looks like you have the tendency to spell "certificate" as "certicate".  Secondly, Podman starts with a capital 'P' unless it's a command example.

Thanks again!
